'Sayafi''\n* ''Dhouk Tohsel''\n* ''The Crocodile''\n* ''[[Lab\u00e8s]]''\n* ''Chich Bich''\n* ''Ma Binetna''\n* ''Abdelli Showtime''\n}}\n\n== Theater ==\n* [[2006]] : ''[[Borj Eddalou]]'' by [[Taoufik El Ayeb]]\n* [[2009]] : ''[[Made in Tunisia]]''\n* [[2015]] : ''[[Abdelli Best Of Show]]''\n* [[2019]] : ''[[Just Abdelli 100% Tabou]]''\n\n== Prices Received ==\n* Price of [[The Best Masculin Interpretation]] / [[Cinematographic Days of Carthage]] [[2006]]\n\n* Best Actor in a Narrative Feature / [[Tribeca Film Festival]] [[2007]]\n\n* Price of The [[Best Comedian FIFA]] [[2007]] / [[International Festival of Love Film]] [[2007]]\n\n* Price of The [[Best Masculine Interpretation]] / [[FESPACO of Burkina]] [[2007]]\n\n* Special Mention / [[International Movie Mediterranean Cinema Festival of Tatouan]] [[2007]]\n\n* Best Masculin Price Interpretation / [[Taormina Film Festival]] [[2007]]\n\n* Major Actor / [[Mostra de Valencia of cinema]] [[2007]]\n\n* Best Actor Award / [[Asian & Arab Competition NEW DELHI]] [[2007]]\n\n* Best Masculin Actor Price / [[International Festival of Muscat]] [[2008]]\n\nBest Actor Price acteur in 2015 for his interpretation in the film Borders of The Sky of [[Far\u00e8s Na\u00e2na\u00e2]] during his Twelfth [[International Film Festival of Duba\u00ef]].\n\nIn [[2015]] et [[2016]], [[Lotfi Abdelli]] received the price of the Best Comedian for his role Bolice & the price of the ramadanesque star in Romdhane Awards, attribued by [[Mosa\u00efque FM]].\n\n* [[January 2019]] : [[Lotfi Abdeli]] won the price of [[Celebrity Awards]] \u00ab Best Tunisian Actor in [[2018]] \u00bb \n\nProjets in progress:\n[[Lotfi Abdelli]] play in a new Sitcom entitled \u2018Al-Jassous\u2019(The spy). This new humorous will be broadcasted on the Channel [[Attessia TV]] during the month of [[Ramadan 2020]].\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{commons-inline|Category:Lotfi Abdelli|Lotfi Abdelli}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Abde